776
01:16:56,120 --> 01:16:57,997
To je Roksen.

777
01:16:58,640 --> 01:17:00,619
Vratio sam se!

778
01:17:01,960 --> 01:17:04,940
Našao sam aspirin.
- Sjajno.

779
01:17:13,320 --> 01:17:14,958
