807
01:19:28,922 --> 01:19:30,051
Cuti!

808
01:19:30,080 --> 01:19:33,629
Šta?

809
01:19:39,880 --> 01:19:42,405
Jesi li dobro?
Brajane?

810
01:19:42,440 --> 01:19:48,106
Da dobro sam,
sve je u redu.

811
01:19:49,880 --> 01:19:52,371
Znaš... mislim da cu da idem.

812
01:19:52,400 --> 01:19:54,436
Šta?

813
01:19:54,440 --> 01:19:57,420
