u redu?

843
01:21:33,859 --> 01:21:37,031
MOlim vas malo tiše,
imamo goste gorre.

844
01:21:37,080 --> 01:21:41,484
Idemo da pricamo.
- Ne idem nigde ocu taksi!

845
01:21:41,519 --> 01:21:45,889
Ne treba ti taksi, sad
cemo razgovarati.

846
01:21:45,920 --> 01:21:47,148
Molim vas malo tiše.

847
01:21:47,160 --> 01:21:49,371
U redu ali idsi, ja pricam
sa ženom!

848
01:21:49,406 --> 01:21:51,582
Ajde da idemo
napolje da ne smetamo

849
01:21:51,960 --> 01:21:53,803
gostima, ja sam
ovde stalno, molim te...

850
01:21:53,838 --> 01:21:55,495
