Vidi šta sam napravio!

853
01:22:08,120 --> 01:22:10,361
Loren!

854
01:22:26,360 --> 01:22:28,191
Loren stani!

855
01:22:32,680 --> 01:22:35,148
Vrati se, prestani!

856
01:23:17,800 --> 01:23:21,588
Povredila sam se.
- A sad ti trebam a?

857
01:23:22,600 --> 01:23:24,249
Molim te...

858
01:23:30,720 --> 01:23:32,506
