859
01:24:02,120 --> 01:24:03,815
Idemo!

860
01:24:14,880 --> 01:24:16,859
Možete li da dodete
u stanicu sutra?

861
01:24:18,000 --> 01:24:20,002
Doci cu.

862
01:24:21,000 --> 01:24:23,389
Sredicu da vas
neko odveze kuci.

863
01:24:42,440 --> 01:24:44,169
I moj otac...

864
01:24:47,440 --> 01:24:49,385
Ne mogu da verujem.

865
01:24:49,420 --> 01:24:50,964
Žao mi je.

866
01:24:51,520 --> 01:24:55,752
On gubi svest, ali u
lucidnim momentima...

867
01:24:56,440 --> 01:24:57,925
Sve anm je rekao.

868
01:24:57,960 --> 01:25:00,918
Srecni ste što ste živi.

869
01:25:02,040 --> 01:25:04,008
