da nam se približi.

870
01:25:04,560 --> 01:25:07,085
Kako nisam videla?

871
01:25:07,120 --> 01:25:10,339
Na žalost niko
nije video.

872
01:25:10,340 --> 01:25:13,559
Ludaci dobro
kriju svoje ludilo.

873
01:25:14,920 --> 01:25:16,888
Zahvaljujuci vama i vašem

874
01:25:16,889 --> 01:25:18,856
ocu Amanda Vitmen
ce biti slobodna.

875
01:25:19,320 --> 01:25:21,413
Spasili ste joj život.

876
01:25:22,000 --> 01:25:24,195
Hvala vam.

877
01:25:24,200 --> 01:25:28,500
I posle toga se okreneš.

878
01:25:28,520 --> 01:25:30,579
Bravo devojke.

879
01:25:31,360 --> 01:25:34,193
Sidni! Tu je.

880
01:25:35,400 --> 01:25:37,698
Mama!

881
01:25:39,480 --> 01:25:42,040
Dušo moja.

882
01:25:54,320 --> 01:25:56,094
Nedostajala si mi.

883
01:25:59,680 --> 01:26:02,285
Ne znam kako da vam
zahvalim. - Ne morate.

